/****************************************************
 * T√äN D·ª∞ √ÅN: REMOTE SMART ESP32-S3 (CH·ªà CH·∫†Y WEB / MILLIS)
 * T√çNH NƒÇNG:
 * - PHI√äN B·∫¢N v8.1: (Theo y√™u c·∫ßu ng∆∞·ªùi d√πng)
 * - ƒê√É B·ªé: SinricPro.
 * - ƒê√É B·ªé: Th·ªùi gian th·∫≠t (NTP).
 * - GI·ªÆ NGUY√äN: Web Server, WiFi Manager, OTA.
 * - GI·ªÆ NGUY√äN: Trang h·∫πn gi·ªù 3 Ch√¢n (4, 5, 7), 3 L·ªãch, H:M:S.
 * - LOGIC H·∫∏N GI·ªú: D·ª±a tr√™n th·ªùi gian ch·∫°y (millis), l·∫∑p l·∫°i m·ªói 24 gi·ªù.
 *
 * - [C·∫¨P NH·∫¨T v8.1]:
 * - N√∫t "Kh·ªüi ƒë·ªông l·∫°i" (Web) v√† (V·∫≠t l√Ω) s·∫Ω B·∫¨T T·ª∞ ƒê·ªòNG
 * v√† KH·ªûI ƒê·ªòNG L·∫†I ESP32 ƒë·ªÉ reset chu k·ª≥ 24 gi·ªù.
 *
 * KI·∫æN TR√öC L√ïI:
 * - L√µi 1 (Core 1): Ch·ªâ ch·∫°y Web Server.
 * - L√µi 0 (Core 0): Ch·∫°y Task logic t·ª± ƒë·ªông (autoControl) 1 gi√¢y/l·∫ßn.
 ****************************************************/

